The soundbar is a great solution for your high-performance audio needs, let you enjoy at home as if you are on the Cinema Scene!
  • Cinematic 3D Surround Sound - With built-in DSP technology present audio with rousing highs and deep lows, makes the sound more accurate and the vocals clearer. The soundbars has surround sound system can turn an ordinary TV to a 3D surround sound, OXS S3 home audio sound bars is equipped with four full range speakers. The dynamic bass is achieved through a special port tube reflection to deliver an fantastic cinematic experience, making every movie you watch, unforgettable.
  • 3 Sound Modes via Remote Control - OXS S3 home audio speakers can improve TV sound with multiple preset EQ settings, to get you High-quality musics and get extreme gaming experiences. Also it supports COAXIAL, AUX, OPTICAL wired audio input to connect with the TV/PC. It can also play audio from USB flash drives.

Besides, there is a light guide for connections and equalizer modes on soundbar to help you know the usage status timely. Product description

Sound Bars for TV & Hear Your TV Better

OXS S3 soundbar for TV with stylish design and dialogue enhancement technologysupports bluetooth 5.0, COAXIAL & multi-wired connectionsand you can tune your sound bar to 3 different modes via the remote control.

Immersive 3D Sound Experience

OXS S3 compact home audio sound bars is a 2.0 Channel soundbar, and can produce 3D sound effects that will take you into an immersive space and make your living room into a Home Theater. *Recommended audition distance8.2 - 11.48ft.

OXS S3 Key Features


Full Range And Poweful Bass

The soundbar is designed with 4 full-range speakers and dynamic bass with a special port tube reflection designed to deliver a soft and flexible bass effect.


Two ways to control

You can control the sound bar with remote or directly with feature buttons control on it. The LED indicator shows the current mode you choose. Note: remote control is not compatible with universal or TV remotes.


Multiple Connections

The OXS S3 TV speakers supports USB flash drive, AUX, OPTICAL, and COAXIAL wired audio input for TV. With Bluetooth 5.0 wireless transmission, you can easily connect OXS S3 to wireless devices .

Movie Mode

Make Your Home Theater

OXS S3 TV speakers sound bar can increase the stereo and layering of movie audio with DSP digital audio processing technology.

Game/News Mode

Rich Sound Configured For Gaming

The entire game scene naturally expands, filling the entire real space, making the limit between real and virtual no longer exist.

Music Mode

Make Your Immersive Concert

OXS S3 speakers for TV will make sure you won't miss a single note in any musical performance and make you immersive concert.

User Tips

When you use optical or coaxial cable to connect the soundbar to a TV, DVD, Blu-ray player or other suitable equipment, please change the Audio Output Settings of TV, DVD, Blu-ray player into the PCM form.

      Now I'm not a tech person and I haven't used any other sound bar before so I can't compare one to another, but this does a pretty good job. First it does come with all the cords so don't be like me and buy another optical cord thinking it wouldn't have... See more
      Now I'm not a tech person and I haven't used any other sound bar before so I can't compare one to another, but this does a pretty good job. First it does come with all the cords so don't be like me and buy another optical cord thinking it wouldn't have it, because mine did. Now it is not a very long cord so if you're planning to have it farther from your tv (like on a different shelf on a stand, etc) you may want to buy a longer cord. Since I've never hooked one up I was worried I wouldn't know how. It took me a min to find the right plugs in the back being it's an older flat screen, but I did and hooked up all the cords within about 2 mins. The bar itself is a little heavy, and bulky. As you can see in the pic it is almost as long as my TV and does take a good chunk of the front of my stand up. Once hooked up the sound for us is good and we can hear our shows much better. I didn't have my TV speakers turned to audio so when I went to mute the sound I'd have to do both the bar and TV so make sure you turn your TV speakers to Audio so that it just comes through the bar. Again I'm sure there are sleeker speakers out there that aren't as big and maybe have better sound but this was a great price and does what we want so for now we are happy.

      3.0 out of 5 starsVerified Purchase
      Spend more!
      Reviewed in the United States on August 7, 2023
      Style: S3
      This is better than no bar but lesson learned..you do indeed get what you pay for in sound bar world. I'll admit it was my first (sound bar that is) but I read myself blind with reviews and this one got raves for days. "Better than the Sony" etc etc.... See more
      This is better than no bar but lesson learned..you do indeed get what you pay for in sound bar world.
      I'll admit it was my first (sound bar that is) but I read myself blind with reviews and this one got raves for days. "Better than the Sony" etc etc.
      Here's my humble list of things to know even for a beginner.
      WATTS matter. This one is low.
      No on screen volume display (super annoying). Only 3 types of sound settings and zero control of base and trebble.
      Lastly it is not compatible with any remote so you have to have 2-3 remotes out all the time.
      The sound quality isn't bad....it's simply just one bump up from the out-of-the-box tin can tv sound....and I'm not picky! It sounds like I am..but I'm not. I'd say spend another $50 and get WATTS and control of your sound at the very least.
